    "The disease region detection module completes the task of detecting the disease region.",
    "The second and third modules complete the interpretation task.",
    "The purpose of the interpretation task is to generate a textual description of the disease image features.",
    "The purpose of the classification task is to train a classifier that can identify categories of plant diseases.",
    "Finally, the name of the disease corresponding to the image is displayed."
